created: 2026-04-19, last updated: 2026-05-07, [Read more](https://tessl.io/registry/skills/github/apideck-libraries/api-skills/onedrive)

OneDrive integration via Apideck's File Storage unified API — same methods work across every connector in File Storage, switch by changing `serviceId`.
Use when the user wants to read, write, upload, or search files, folders, and drives in OneDrive.
Routes through Apideck with serviceId "onedrive".
...
Access OneDrive through Apideck's **File Storage** unified API — one of 5 File Storage connectors that share the same method surface.
...
Activate this skill when the user explicitly wants to work with **OneDrive** — for example, "upload a file in OneDrive" or "list a folder in OneDrive".
